00:14:26,560 --> 00:14:30,320
NATIONAL HIGH SCHOOL
MEN'S TENNIS LEAGUE

262
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:34,760
[Yu Qing students] Go, Yu Qing, go!

263
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:39,200
Go, Yu Qing, go!

264
00:14:39,280 --> 00:14:43,640
Go, Yu Qing, go!

265
00:14:43,720 --> 00:14:48,160
Go, Yu Qing, go!

266
00:14:48,240 --> 00:14:49,480
[umpire 3] The match begins.

267
00:14:50,040 --> 00:14:51,560
Lu Xia from Yu Qing will serve.

268
00:14:52,560 --> 00:14:54,560
[action music]

269
00:14:57,800 --> 00:15:00,080
[ball whooshing]

270
00:15:02,800 --> 00:15:03,960
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

271
00:15:11,560 --> 00:15:13,960
[thwacking]

272
00:15:16,400 --> 00:15:17,400
[sighs]

273
00:15:18,640 --> 00:15:20,240
Have you gotten anything?

274
00:15:20,600 --> 00:15:21,520
[Yue scoffs]

275
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:23,560
Yan Zhiming, right?

276
00:15:23,920 --> 00:15:25,840
Are you the coach of Guo Zi High School?

277
00:15:28,320 --> 00:15:29,400
I'm Guan Yue.

278
00:15:30,040 --> 00:15:31,800
I've never had anyone
recognize me as that.

279
00:15:32,320 --> 00:15:33,800
I'm a little flattered.

280
00:15:34,400 --> 00:15:36,360
Don't you have to cheer for your team?

281
00:15:36,960 --> 00:15:38,960
They should have won by now.

282
00:15:39,560 --> 00:15:41,080
Second doubles, 6-3.

283
00:15:41,640 --> 00:15:43,200
First doubles, 6-2.

284
00:15:43,720 --> 00:15:45,360
Third singles, 6-1.

285
00:15:45,960 --> 00:15:47,960
In order to play against you
in the future,

286
00:15:49,720 --> 00:15:50,920
we will work hard.

287
00:15:51,600 --> 00:15:52,880
I have to remind you.

288
00:15:54,160 --> 00:15:56,760
On the court, nothing is guaranteed.

289
00:15:57,320 --> 00:16:00,240
If you make a mistake, you're out.

290
00:16:00,880 --> 00:16:02,600
That is why...

291
00:16:03,160 --> 00:16:04,440
I've always been careful.

292
00:16:04,520 --> 00:16:05,680
Over-confidence...

293
00:16:06,640 --> 00:16:07,640
is not a good thing.

294
00:16:08,360 --> 00:16:09,880
Looks like you're rather concerned.

295
00:16:10,440 --> 00:16:12,040
You're reminding me about so many things.

296
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:16,480
I shall return the favor
and make a prediction for Yu Qing's match.

297
00:16:17,160 --> 00:16:19,360
[Yue] They should be having
the third singles match now.

298
00:16:19,880 --> 00:16:22,160
Lu Xia should win with a score of 6-0.

299
00:16:22,240 --> 00:16:26,120
So, Yu Qing would win
with a total score of 3-0.

300
00:16:26,560 --> 00:16:27,600
Before the match,

301
00:16:27,680 --> 00:16:30,480
you told Jin Qiu High School
our weaknesses, right?

302
00:16:31,480 --> 00:16:34,520
It seems like you also know that,
even if they knew our weaknesses,

303
00:16:35,200 --> 00:16:36,760
they're still no match for Yu Qing.

304
00:16:37,560 --> 00:16:40,880
That team is just hopeless.

305
00:16:41,400 --> 00:16:43,200
However, Guo Zi High School

306
00:16:43,600 --> 00:16:44,800
is different.

307
00:16:45,320 --> 00:16:48,000
So, you wanted to find out

308
00:16:48,640 --> 00:16:50,480
how we would react to an opponent

309
00:16:51,040 --> 00:16:52,120
