you could learn even more.

312
00:16:55,760 --> 00:16:57,000
Am I right?

313
00:16:57,560 --> 00:17:00,760
I did not break any rules.

314
00:17:01,400 --> 00:17:02,520
[Yan Zhiming scoffs]

315
00:17:05,720 --> 00:17:09,160
Let's look forward to our future matches.

