00:17:11,079 --> 00:17:11,960
[snickers]

317
00:17:16,839 --> 00:17:18,920
[thwacking]

318
00:17:19,760 --> 00:17:20,760
End of match.

319
00:17:20,839 --> 00:17:22,839
Yu Qing High School wins
with a score of 6-0.

320
00:17:23,359 --> 00:17:25,480
[students cheering]

321
00:17:26,960 --> 00:17:29,400
[announcer] Guo Zi High School versus
Hong Ye Hu High School.

322
00:17:29,960 --> 00:17:31,880
