333
00:18:09,480 --> 00:18:10,960
The roads here all look the same.

334
00:18:11,960 --> 00:18:13,640
Captain is going to
make you run laps later.

335
00:18:13,720 --> 00:18:14,720
Qiao Chen.

336
00:18:15,200 --> 00:18:16,520
[Peng and Ying panting]

337
00:18:16,600 --> 00:18:18,240
Finally, a familiar face.

338
00:18:18,320 --> 00:18:19,800
[Peng] There are too many courts here.

339
00:18:20,200 --> 00:18:22,480
-The roads here all look the same.
-[Peng] Mm-hm.

340
00:18:22,560 --> 00:18:23,440
Really?

341
00:18:24,000 --> 00:18:24,880
What is it?

342
00:18:26,080 --> 00:18:27,440
Nothing. Let's go.

343
00:18:28,640 --> 00:18:29,520
Where?

344
00:18:29,600 --> 00:18:31,240
We agreed to watch Yu Feng play.

345
00:18:31,320 --> 00:18:32,960
Qiao Chen, I have to practice.

346
00:18:33,840 --> 00:18:35,760
Why can't you just follow the team?

347
00:18:37,480 --> 00:18:39,000
[Yu Feng student 1] Go, Yu Feng, go!

348
00:18:39,080 --> 00:18:40,920
[Yu Feng student 2] Yu Feng,
the champions!

349
00:18:41,000 --> 00:18:45,800
[Yu Feng students] Go for it! Yu Feng!

350
00:18:45,880 --> 00:18:47,240
Who won?

351
00:18:47,320 --> 00:18:48,920
Yu Feng, of course.

352
00:18:49,000 --> 00:18:50,840
Now, Yu Feng is no longer a dark horse.

353
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:52,800
They're a reputable team now.

354
00:18:52,880 --> 00:18:54,040
I know, right?

355
00:18:54,120 --> 00:18:58,360
We have to let Lu Xia learn from them
so that he can improve even faster.

356
00:18:58,440 --> 00:18:59,560
Right, Lu Xia?

357
00:19:00,400 --> 00:19:01,280
Lu Xia?

358
00:19:02,040 --> 00:19:03,040
[Peng and Ying] Huh?

359
00:19:03,600 --> 00:19:04,520
Huh?

360
00:19:05,680 --> 00:19:06,960
Where did that kid go again?

361
00:19:08,040 --> 00:19:08,960
[Peng] Hm?

362
00:19:11,400 --> 00:19:12,360
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

363
00:19:12,800 --> 00:19:13,800
[groans]

364
00:19:14,400 --> 00:19:18,000
[crowd cheers]

365
00:19:18,080 --> 00:19:20,840
NATIONAL HIGH SCHOOL MEN'S TENNIS LEAGUE
YU FENG VS 55TH HIGH SCHOOL

366
00:19:21,640 --> 00:19:23,040
[panting]

367
00:19:24,240 --> 00:19:25,240
You're fast.

368
00:19:28,040 --> 00:19:29,000
[snickers]

369
00:19:31,520 --> 00:19:32,440
[Weiming pants]

370
00:19:34,400 --> 00:19:36,800
Compared to when we played against them,

371
00:19:37,120 --> 00:19:38,440
Yu Feng has grown stronger.

372
00:19:38,520 --> 00:19:41,440
Indeed. Shen Weiming has gotten faster.

373
00:19:41,880 --> 00:19:44,280
[Sha] The 55th High players
could barely keep up.

374
00:19:44,680 --> 00:19:46,480
But Shen Weiming hardly broke a sweat.

375
00:19:46,840 --> 00:19:48,200
It's the same for us.

376
00:19:48,560 --> 00:19:49,960
If we don't improve,

377
00:19:50,520 --> 00:19:52,480
we will be left behind.

378
00:19:55,920 --> 00:19:56,800
Actually,

379
00:19:57,440 --> 00:19:59,880
going by your performance today,
Yu Qing has improved a lot.

380
00:19:59,960 --> 00:20:01,440
Don't stress yourselves out.

381
00:20:01,520 --> 00:20:02,520
[Tang Jiale] Mm-hm.

382
00:20:03,120 --> 00:20:04,560
If we have to play against Yu Feng,

383
00:20:05,200 --> 00:20:07,000
it's going to be a tough match.

384
00:20:07,560 --> 00:20:10,560
[comical music]

385
00:20:17,400 --> 00:20:19,640
Peng Xiang, hurry up.

386
00:20:19,720 --> 00:20:21,120
They've all gone back for the match.

387
00:20:21,200 --> 00:20:22,440
What's the hurry?

388
00:20:22,520 --> 00:20:24,360
I'm getting more drinks for them.

389
00:20:25,040 --> 00:20:27,200
We need some time to find our way there.

390
00:20:27,280 --> 00:20:28,280
[soda bottle clatters]

391
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:31,240
Lu Xia likes this drink.

392
00:20:31,640 --> 00:20:33,160
[Peng chuckles]

393
00:20:33,840 --> 00:20:35,520
[soda can thuds, clatters]

394
00:20:36,840 --> 00:20:38,280
May I have one, too?

395
00:20:38,640 --> 00:20:39,560
Xu Xing Zi!

396
00:20:39,800 --> 00:20:41,320
Isn't your brother competing?

397
00:20:41,400 --> 00:20:42,560
Why are you here?

398
00:20:42,640 --> 00:20:44,840
There's nothing to worry about.

399
00:20:44,920 --> 00:20:47,160
Shen Weiming
already has full control of the match.

400
00:20:48,160 --> 00:20:49,520
Who is Shen Weiming?

401
00:20:50,240 --> 00:20:53,600
He's the one who was defeated by Baiyang
in the last competition.

402
00:20:53,680 --> 00:20:55,680
Oh! He's a really good player.

403
00:20:55,960 --> 00:20:57,080
[Ying gasps]

404
00:20:57,640 --> 00:20:59,800
[chuckles]
It's okay.

405
00:21:00,400 --> 00:21:01,440
[laughs]

406
00:21:01,800 --> 00:21:03,840
-This is for you.
-Thanks.

407
00:21:03,920 --> 00:21:06,360
We will not lose next time. See you later.

408
00:21:06,440 --> 00:21:07,560
-Bye.
-[Peng] Mm.

409
00:21:11,080 --> 00:21:12,800
[grunts]
Don't run your mouth.

410
00:21:13,160 --> 00:21:14,240
[sighs]

411
00:21:15,080 --> 00:21:15,960
[Ying] Hurry up.

412
00:21:20,160 --> 00:21:23,600
Can you stop eating?
Can you just stop eating, huh?

413
00:21:24,120 --> 00:21:25,440
Stretchers take two men to carry.

414
00:21:25,520 --> 00:21:26,480
You need to help me.

415
00:21:26,560 --> 00:21:28,760
Can't you show some team spirit, huh?

416
00:21:29,200 --> 00:21:30,480
-Sure...
-Aunt Sha.

417
00:21:31,760 --> 00:21:33,520
I'll give you another chance. Try again.

418
00:21:33,600 --> 00:21:35,160
[Huang Jing] "Miss."

419
00:21:35,600 --> 00:21:37,120
Miss Sha.

420
00:21:38,080 --> 00:21:38,960
What's up?

421
00:21:39,840 --> 00:21:43,440
Aren't you one of our supporters?

422
00:21:43,520 --> 00:21:45,200
Why are you filming other people?

423
00:21:45,280 --> 00:21:46,360
Kid.

424
00:21:46,960 --> 00:21:48,360
I'm here for work.

425
00:21:48,680 --> 00:21:49,760
Out of my way.

426
00:21:49,840 --> 00:21:51,480
I don't eat all day like you.

427
00:21:52,400 --> 00:21:53,520
[Sha] Hold this for me.

428
00:21:58,920 --> 00:22:01,080
Hey, isn't this the picture
we took last time?

429
00:22:03,560 --> 00:22:05,120
What's this button for?

430
00:22:05,200 --> 00:22:06,040
Formatting.

431
00:22:06,120 --> 00:22:07,280
FORMATTING MEMORY CARD

432
00:22:07,360 --> 00:22:08,360
[Xiuwen] Hm?

433
00:22:09,280 --> 00:22:10,400
FORMATTING COMPLETED

434
00:22:10,720 --> 00:22:11,840
[Huang Jing clears throat]

435
00:22:14,800 --> 00:22:15,680
Uh...

436
00:22:19,320 --> 00:22:21,080
[Huang Jing sighs]

437
00:22:25,680 --> 00:22:26,640
Ma Xiuwen, Huang Jing.

438
00:22:26,720 --> 00:22:27,920
[Xiuwen whimpers]

439
00:22:28,640 --> 00:22:32,040
[breathing deeply]

440
00:22:32,120 --> 00:22:34,280
Work is more important. Ignore them.

441
00:22:36,840 --> 00:22:37,720
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

442
00:22:38,200 --> 00:22:39,160
[pants, groans]

443
00:22:39,760 --> 00:22:42,360
[crowd cheers]

444
00:22:48,200 --> 00:22:51,800
I didn't expect to be defeated
by such an unremarkable school.

445
00:22:51,880 --> 00:22:53,840
[55th High School student]
Well, in the next match,

446
00:22:53,920 --> 00:22:55,280
you'll be playing against Xing Yao.

447
00:22:55,800 --> 00:22:56,920
Try not to lose too badly.

448
00:22:58,800 --> 00:23:00,440
Whoever our opponent is,

449
00:23:01,120 --> 00:23:02,280
Yu Feng will not cower.

450
00:23:08,320 --> 00:23:09,400
[snickers]

451
00:23:10,520 --> 00:23:12,720
[Weiming] It's all right.
It's all right. Hm.

452
00:23:15,800 --> 00:23:18,040
[sighs]
I'm excited for the Xing Yao match.

453
00:23:18,400 --> 00:23:21,120
I can't wait for Ji Jingwu
to know who I am.

454
00:23:22,200 --> 00:23:23,720
You've met Ji Jingwu?

455
00:23:25,440 --> 00:23:27,680
[sighs]
I have.

456
00:23:28,120 --> 00:23:29,000
And...

457
00:23:30,600 --> 00:23:32,840
-You lost?
-Yes.

458
00:23:32,920 --> 00:23:33,960
I didn't win.

459
00:23:34,040 --> 00:23:36,000
Who said you could
play against him in private?

460
00:23:37,880 --> 00:23:39,440
I just ran into him.

461
00:23:39,920 --> 00:23:41,880
I didn't want to disgrace Yu Feng.

462
00:23:42,280 --> 00:23:43,680
You've disgraced us by losing.

463
00:23:51,480 --> 00:23:52,600
[Qiao Chen] Hey.

464
00:23:54,680 --> 00:23:55,720
Good game.

465
00:23:59,600 --> 00:24:00,680
Where's Shen Weiming?

466
00:24:02,560 --> 00:24:03,400
[Ziping] Um...

467
00:24:05,120 --> 00:24:06,120
He's doing something.

468
00:24:07,720 --> 00:24:08,880
He reflected on

469
00:24:10,160 --> 00:24:11,680
his private match with Xing Yao.

470
00:24:12,320 --> 00:24:13,520
You're involved too, right?

471
00:24:13,960 --> 00:24:15,320
What does it have to do with me?

472
00:24:16,560 --> 00:24:17,440
[chuckles]

473
00:24:18,480 --> 00:24:19,720
Hold on!

474
00:24:20,240 --> 00:24:21,480
[Qiao Chen] Captain Xu Ziping,

475
00:24:22,080 --> 00:24:25,000
with regard to the private match,
please keep it a secret.

476
00:24:25,440 --> 00:24:27,840
[scoffs]
I don't care about other players,

477
00:24:28,240 --> 00:24:29,960
but when my own players
play private matches,

478
00:24:30,040 --> 00:24:32,560
especially before actual matches,
they have to be punished.

479
00:24:32,880 --> 00:24:34,560
Are you preparing
to play against Xing Yao?

480
00:24:34,640 --> 00:24:36,400
-Mm-hm.
-[Qiao Chen] Please remember this.

481
00:24:36,480 --> 00:24:38,880
Help me and your sister
teach Ji Jingwu a lesson.

482
00:24:39,720 --> 00:24:42,120
I just heard from Weiming.
Thanks for helping her.

483
00:24:42,200 --> 00:24:44,120
[scoffs]
That's nothing.

484
00:24:44,440 --> 00:24:47,720
I've known Xing Zi
since you transferred in two years ago.

485
00:24:47,800 --> 00:24:51,680
Furthermore, Yu Qing and Yu Feng
have always had each other's backs.

486
00:24:52,400 --> 00:24:54,280
Lending a hand is nothing.

487
00:24:54,360 --> 00:24:55,560
Don't mention it.

488
00:24:56,040 --> 00:24:56,880
Thank you, anyway.

489
00:24:56,960 --> 00:24:58,080
You're welcome.

490
00:24:58,320 --> 00:24:59,440
Qiao Chen.

491
00:25:01,200 --> 00:25:03,600
-Captain.
-Are you Yu Qing's diplomat?

492
00:25:04,000 --> 00:25:06,080
"Have each other's back",
"lending a hand..."

493
00:25:06,600 --> 00:25:08,720
Are you just saying things
you learned in school?

494
00:25:09,000 --> 00:25:10,120
It's none of your business.

495
00:25:12,280 --> 00:25:13,360
Xu Ziping.

496
00:25:15,160 --> 00:25:17,320
Congratulations on your win
against 55th High.

497
00:25:17,960 --> 00:25:18,800
Thank you.

498
00:25:19,160 --> 00:25:20,640
You can take a break now.

499
00:25:20,720 --> 00:25:22,320
Mm-hm. We'll go ahead.

500
00:25:22,400 --> 00:25:23,480
All right.

501
00:25:29,120 --> 00:25:31,240
[Yan Zhiming] They transferred in
two years ago.

502
00:25:31,320 --> 00:25:32,360
In that case,

503
00:25:32,760 --> 00:25:34,120
Xu Ziping was...

504
00:25:34,240 --> 00:25:35,400
[Siyang] Qiao Chen.

505
00:25:37,400 --> 00:25:39,520
Did you play a private match
with Xing Yao?

506
00:25:39,960 --> 00:25:42,520
Captain, you've heard?

507
00:25:42,600 --> 00:25:44,760
You don't need to be told
what to do now, right?

508
00:25:45,440 --> 00:25:47,640
I know. I violated club rules.

509
00:25:47,920 --> 00:25:50,000
I'll do extra training.
I won't do it again.

510
00:25:50,440 --> 00:25:51,520
It's good that you know.

511
00:25:51,600 --> 00:25:53,840
That punishment is nothing
but a reminder for you.

512
00:25:54,320 --> 00:25:58,080
Since we now know how strong Xing Yao is,
we need to train extra hard.

513
00:25:59,160 --> 00:26:02,800
I wonder how they've changed
since last year.

514
00:26:03,960 --> 00:26:05,000
Just as well,

515
00:26:05,480 --> 00:26:08,200
let's watch Xing Yao's match
later in the afternoon.

516
00:26:08,320 --> 00:26:15,320
[Xing Yao students] Xing Yao!

517
00:26:18,120 --> 00:26:19,880
[cheering continues]

518
00:26:21,080 --> 00:26:22,200
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

519
00:26:22,280 --> 00:26:24,400
NATIONAL HIGH SCHOOL MEN'S TENNIS LEAGUE
KAI LIN INTERNATIONAL VS XING YAO

520
00:26:24,800 --> 00:26:25,720
End of match.

521
00:26:25,800 --> 00:26:27,960
[umpire 4] Xing Yao High School wins
with a score of 6-0.

522
00:26:29,360 --> 00:26:31,160
HU LIANGLIANG
XING YAO HIGH SCHOOL, PLAYER

523
00:26:38,200 --> 00:26:42,640
[Xing Yao students] Xing Yao!

524
00:26:45,120 --> 00:26:46,960
[indistinct cheering]

525
00:26:47,320 --> 00:26:48,680
The match ended so quickly.

526
00:26:49,840 --> 00:26:51,880
Interesting. They only lasted 15 minutes.

527
00:26:51,960 --> 00:26:56,920
[Xing Yao students] Xing Yao!

528
00:27:01,840 --> 00:27:02,760
Captain.

529
00:27:03,280 --> 00:27:04,600
What's wrong with you?

530
00:27:06,680 --> 00:27:08,920
You should have finished them off
in ten minutes.

531
00:27:10,920 --> 00:27:12,160
If it was me,

532
00:27:12,960 --> 00:27:14,160
I wouldn't even need five.

533
00:27:14,240 --> 00:27:19,960
[cheering continues]

534
00:27:24,440 --> 00:27:25,400
Hey.

535
00:27:25,480 --> 00:27:27,600
Lu Xia, what took you so long?
Where have you been?

536
00:27:27,680 --> 00:27:28,560
Practicing.

537
00:27:29,120 --> 00:27:30,040
I see.

538
00:27:31,040 --> 00:27:32,840
[Dayong] In our match
with Xing Yao last year,

539
00:27:33,280 --> 00:27:34,880
the weather was like today's.

540
00:27:35,400 --> 00:27:36,400
That's right.

541
00:27:38,040 --> 00:27:39,640
[Dayong] They also had many supporters.

542
00:27:40,520 --> 00:27:41,560
Sadly, in that competition,

543
00:27:42,480 --> 00:27:43,560
even after four matches,

544
00:27:43,960 --> 00:27:45,360
we only won one.

545
00:27:47,840 --> 00:27:50,800
Yu Qing's journey to the nationals
came to an end.

546
00:27:50,880 --> 00:27:52,880
[somber music]

547
00:27:52,960 --> 00:27:54,600
[panting]

548
00:27:54,680 --> 00:27:56,120
[Dayong] The only match we won

549
00:27:56,440 --> 00:27:58,680
was played by Siyang,
who hadn't become the captain then.

550
00:27:59,000 --> 00:28:01,120
He gave that singles match his all.

551
00:28:03,320 --> 00:28:04,360
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

552
00:28:06,520 --> 00:28:07,480
[Jingwu gasps]

553
00:28:11,840 --> 00:28:14,240
JI JINGWU, XING YAO - 5
MU SIYANG, YU QING - 7

554
00:28:15,880 --> 00:28:17,560
[Dayong] However,
for that moment of glory,

555
00:28:17,880 --> 00:28:19,840
he paid an unimaginable price.

556
00:28:20,720 --> 00:28:22,720
[somber music]

557
00:28:29,760 --> 00:28:32,960
[Dayong] Even now,
none of us expected that...

558
00:28:35,440 --> 00:28:37,760
what happened would have
such a huge impact

559
00:28:38,920 --> 00:28:40,560
on both Siyang and the team.

560
00:28:43,360 --> 00:28:45,280
[Dahe] We third years
are ending our journey here.

561
00:28:45,360 --> 00:28:48,080
I know I haven't been a good captain,
but I'm passing the title to you.

562
00:28:48,160 --> 00:28:49,040
HAO DAHE
FORMER CAPTAIN OF YU QING

563
00:28:49,320 --> 00:28:51,440
The responsibility is yours now.

564
00:28:51,920 --> 00:28:53,920
[light music]

565
00:28:54,200 --> 00:28:57,080
Everyone is obliged to make it to
the top eight of the nationals next year.

566
00:28:57,160 --> 00:28:59,440
Run back to school with Siyang.

567
00:28:59,520 --> 00:29:00,920
[Dahe] Start training immediately.

568
00:29:01,120 --> 00:29:03,680
Captain, thank you...

569
00:29:04,840 --> 00:29:05,920
for the last two years.

570
00:29:06,480 --> 00:29:07,440
[chuckles]

571
00:29:07,520 --> 00:29:09,560
-[all] Thank you, Captain.
-[Yan Zhiming] Thank you.

572
00:29:15,440 --> 00:29:16,400
Hm.

573
00:29:18,440 --> 00:29:21,000
Now, everybody,
run with me back to school.

574
00:29:21,760 --> 00:29:22,760
Let's go.

575
00:29:23,120 --> 00:29:23,960
Mm-hm.

576
00:29:34,000 --> 00:29:37,040
[Xing Yao students] Xing Yao!

577
00:29:37,120 --> 00:29:38,920
However,
this year is different from last year.

578
00:29:39,000 --> 00:29:41,280
This year, we will win.

579
00:29:41,360 --> 00:29:43,480
-[Xing Yao students] Xing Yao. Xing Yao.
-Mm-hm.

580
00:29:43,560 --> 00:29:44,960
Because we are all different now.

581
00:29:49,160 --> 00:29:51,400
All right, let's go back.

582
00:29:51,480 --> 00:29:53,240
Let's prepare well
for the upcoming matches.

583
00:29:53,800 --> 00:29:58,680
[Xing Yao students] Xing Yao!

584
00:29:59,360 --> 00:30:00,280
Let's go.

585
00:30:00,640 --> 00:30:05,040
[Xing Yao students] Xing Yao!

586
00:30:10,080 --> 00:30:12,640
[cheering continues]

587
00:30:14,280 --> 00:30:16,240
[thunder rumbling]

588
00:30:20,960 --> 00:30:23,480
[Yu panting, blows air]

589
00:30:26,040 --> 00:30:27,440
You just finished watching a match?

590
00:30:28,800 --> 00:30:29,720
I'll see you home.

591
00:30:30,840 --> 00:30:34,240
-It's okay. I'll just wait here.
-[thunder rumbling]

592
00:30:34,960 --> 00:30:35,960
If you have time,

593
00:30:36,960 --> 00:30:38,480
you can go home on weekends.

594
00:30:39,440 --> 00:30:41,320
Don't act like you care a lot about me.

595
00:30:41,920 --> 00:30:43,080
If you really do,

596
00:30:43,280 --> 00:30:46,040
play the next match
and let me beat you properly.

597
00:30:48,720 --> 00:30:49,760
I'll see you on the court.

598
00:30:50,720 --> 00:30:52,520
[thunder rumbling]

599
00:31:12,040 --> 00:31:14,040
[light music]

600
00:31:23,360 --> 00:31:24,200
[Peng] Hm?

601
00:31:26,120 --> 00:31:27,440
What are you looking at?

602
00:31:30,840 --> 00:31:33,960
Do you think Lu Xia will notice

603
00:31:34,040 --> 00:31:36,040
that I'm wearing
the same wrist guard as him?

604
00:31:36,120 --> 00:31:37,080
[chuckles]

605
00:31:37,160 --> 00:31:38,800
So that is what you're thinking about.

606
00:31:39,760 --> 00:31:41,960
Shall I give him a hint?

607
00:31:43,720 --> 00:31:44,640
Hm?

608
00:31:44,720 --> 00:31:45,680
No.

609
00:31:46,760 --> 00:31:47,680
Really?

610
00:31:48,560 --> 00:31:49,440
Yes.

611
00:31:50,120 --> 00:31:52,600
-Don't tease me.
-[both laughing]

612
00:31:54,080 --> 00:31:54,960
What if, one day,

613
00:31:55,040 --> 00:31:57,640
when Lu Xia is competing,
he sees you wearing the same wrist guard?

614
00:31:57,720 --> 00:32:01,240
Will he gain a sudden surge of power
and win the match?

615
00:32:03,160 --> 00:32:05,120
[both giggle]

616
00:32:05,760 --> 00:32:08,640
Ying, I do like this wrist guard
quite a bit.

617
00:32:08,720 --> 00:32:10,120
How about you give it to me?

618
00:32:11,520 --> 00:32:13,520
[playful music]

619
00:32:14,200 --> 00:32:15,520
[Ying] Uh...

620
00:32:18,000 --> 00:32:20,400
It doesn't suit you.

621
00:32:20,920 --> 00:32:23,480
I'll get a new one for you later.

622
00:32:23,960 --> 00:32:25,920
So, Lu Xia is more important than me now?

623
00:32:26,600 --> 00:32:28,360
Look, you hesitated.

624
00:32:28,440 --> 00:32:30,680
All right,
he really is more important than me.

625
00:32:32,240 --> 00:32:33,960
-You're still more important.
-[chuckles]

626
00:32:34,040 --> 00:32:35,120
I don't believe you.

627
00:32:35,720 --> 00:32:37,440
-You can look at it.
-I don't want to look.

628
00:32:37,520 --> 00:32:38,440
[both giggle]

629
00:32:42,240 --> 00:32:45,120
♪ My darling ♪

630
00:32:45,640 --> 00:32:47,200
♪ I know ♪

631
00:32:47,280 --> 00:32:50,840
♪ That you're absolutely perfect ♪

632
00:32:51,040 --> 00:32:52,120
[Lu Xia] I'm starving.

633
00:32:53,160 --> 00:32:54,160
You're back, son.

634
00:32:54,440 --> 00:32:55,280
Did you lose again?

635
00:32:55,360 --> 00:32:57,200
Here, try my new creation.

636
00:32:57,280 --> 00:32:59,640
I won, Dad.

637
00:33:00,200 --> 00:33:02,560
Takeaways are not as good as my cooking.

638
00:33:04,440 --> 00:33:06,880
You're a growing boy.
You shouldn't eat junk food!

639
00:33:15,520 --> 00:33:17,880
[students] Goodbye, sir.

640
00:33:20,880 --> 00:33:23,280
[indistinct chatter]

641
00:33:24,240 --> 00:33:26,240
[comical music]

642
00:33:37,040 --> 00:33:39,040
[comical music continues]

643
00:33:51,400 --> 00:33:52,400
What are you doing?

644
00:33:53,560 --> 00:33:54,680
I'm eating.

645
00:33:55,640 --> 00:33:57,000
Do you want a bite?

646
00:33:58,320 --> 00:33:59,520
Explain this.

647
00:34:00,960 --> 00:34:02,280
[laughs]

648
00:34:03,680 --> 00:34:05,960
I'm worried about dirtying
the locker room,

649
00:34:06,040 --> 00:34:08,960
so I borrowed your towels.

650
00:34:09,199 --> 00:34:10,199
[scoffs]

651
00:34:12,760 --> 00:34:15,320
Qiao Chen, you'd better wash them.

652
00:34:16,679 --> 00:34:18,880
I will. Chill out!

653
00:34:19,199 --> 00:34:21,199
Clean them immediately!

654
00:34:21,280 --> 00:34:23,600
What's up with you?
You're acting like a girl!

655
00:34:23,679 --> 00:34:26,520
-Who are you calling a girl?
-You! So what?

656
00:34:26,600 --> 00:34:28,280
Wash them! Right now!

657
00:34:28,360 --> 00:34:30,440
Stop it! What are you doing?

658
00:34:35,080 --> 00:34:37,440
All right,
pack up quickly and go upstairs.

659
00:34:37,520 --> 00:34:38,800
Coach wants to see us.

660
00:34:50,280 --> 00:34:51,960
[Coach Qi] Our opponent
in the quarterfinals

661
00:34:52,040 --> 00:34:53,080
is Guo Zi High School.

662
00:34:53,159 --> 00:34:54,360
If we win this match,

663
00:34:54,679 --> 00:34:56,920
we'll officially be
in the qualifying round.

664
00:34:57,960 --> 00:35:00,159
The line-up for this match
remains largely the same.

665
00:35:00,719 --> 00:35:02,440
Third singles, Lu Xia.

666
00:35:03,520 --> 00:35:05,160
Second singles, Zhuo Zhi.

667
00:35:05,880 --> 00:35:07,520
First singles, Siyang.

668
00:35:09,040 --> 00:35:10,840
First doubles, the Golden Partners.

669
00:35:11,720 --> 00:35:13,600
Second doubles, Qiao Chen.

670
00:35:14,120 --> 00:35:15,160
Here.

671
00:35:15,240 --> 00:35:16,880
And Baiyang.

672
00:35:17,720 --> 00:35:19,160
-Huh?
-Doubles?

673
00:35:19,560 --> 00:35:20,920
With him?

674
00:35:21,560 --> 00:35:23,080
-[Tang Jiale chuckles]
-[sucks teeth]

675
00:35:23,560 --> 00:35:24,520
[Coach Qi chuckles]

676
00:35:25,440 --> 00:35:28,080
Yan Zhiming, your turn.

677
00:35:28,160 --> 00:35:29,160
Okay.

678
00:35:34,640 --> 00:35:36,640
[comical music]

679
00:35:39,920 --> 00:35:42,800
Yan, what's with the suspense?

680
00:35:43,440 --> 00:35:44,680
[shushes]

681
00:35:44,760 --> 00:35:46,120
I'm looking out for spies.

682
00:35:46,680 --> 00:35:48,280
-[Tang Jiale] Spies?
-[shushes]

683
00:36:01,760 --> 00:36:04,440
[Yan Zhiming] During the last match
against Jin Qiu High School,

684
00:36:04,920 --> 00:36:08,360
you might have noticed
that attacks on our players were targeted.

685
00:36:08,440 --> 00:36:10,880
Each match was difficult.

686
00:36:11,640 --> 00:36:15,360
This is because our rival has not only
gathered information on our players,

687
00:36:16,000 --> 00:36:18,760
but they even knew
how to target our weaknesses.

688
00:36:19,440 --> 00:36:21,000
You're making it sound too serious.

689
00:36:21,080 --> 00:36:22,280
Didn't we win?

690
00:36:27,640 --> 00:36:30,360
This is all because of him,

691
00:36:31,560 --> 00:36:33,880
Guan Yue.

692
00:36:34,400 --> 00:36:35,920
[Yan Zhiming] He's our next rival.

693
00:36:36,000 --> 00:36:38,720
He's the strategist
and the soul of Guo Zi's team.

694
00:36:40,120 --> 00:36:42,640
He's the one
who gathered information on us

695
00:36:43,200 --> 00:36:44,640
and shared it with the Jin Qiu team.

696
00:36:45,520 --> 00:36:48,120
Guan Yue has gathered outstanding players
from different places

697
00:36:48,200 --> 00:36:49,640
to form this new team.

698
00:36:49,880 --> 00:36:51,520
Guo Zi High School supports him.

699
00:36:52,000 --> 00:36:54,680
A lot of good tennis players
have transferred to Guo Zi.

700
00:36:57,240 --> 00:36:59,240
[tense music]

701
00:37:05,160 --> 00:37:06,240
What does that mean?

702
00:37:06,760 --> 00:37:09,760
Does this Guan Yue
intend to steal Zhuo Zhi?

703
00:37:10,520 --> 00:37:11,600
[Yan Zhiming sighs]

704
00:37:12,960 --> 00:37:16,840
Actually, I intend to visit Guo Zi
to find out more.

705
00:37:18,400 --> 00:37:20,960
Zhuo Zhi can go with me if he wants to.

706
00:37:23,280 --> 00:37:24,240
It's okay.

707
00:37:25,360 --> 00:37:29,440
GUO ZI HIGH SCHOOL

708
00:37:43,280 --> 00:37:44,240
Yan.

709
00:37:45,040 --> 00:37:46,880
You've come all the way here
for information.

710
00:37:47,640 --> 00:37:49,160
Are you happy with what you got?

711
00:37:54,040 --> 00:37:55,440
Do you really think

712
00:37:55,880 --> 00:37:58,720
that training hard
is enough to beat Yu Qing?

713
00:37:59,200 --> 00:38:00,840
When it comes to individuals,

714
00:38:01,680 --> 00:38:04,400
we don't have as many outstanding players
as Yu Qing.

715
00:38:05,400 --> 00:38:07,880
But as long as
I know your weaknesses and strategies,

716
00:38:09,040 --> 00:38:10,600
we can still defeat you

717
00:38:11,120 --> 00:38:12,720
with what we have.

718
00:38:13,320 --> 00:38:14,600
You being here doesn't faze me.

719
00:38:14,680 --> 00:38:18,720
After all, the weaknesses I've learned
are not something you could overcome...

720
00:38:19,960 --> 00:38:21,560
in a short time.

721
00:38:25,600 --> 00:38:28,360
It seems like
my previous reminders were insufficient.

722
00:38:30,080 --> 00:38:31,840
Even if you possessed certain data,

723
00:38:32,520 --> 00:38:34,040
that doesn't mean you can defeat us.

724
00:38:34,960 --> 00:38:38,160
And I'm speaking from experience.

725
00:38:38,960 --> 00:38:40,560
Let's just wait and see.

726
00:38:43,320 --> 00:38:44,280
[Yan Zhiming snickers]

727
00:38:50,760 --> 00:38:51,720
[thwacks]

728
00:38:52,960 --> 00:38:56,280
[Yu grunting]

729
00:38:58,120 --> 00:38:59,640
-[thwacks]
-[thumps]

730
00:39:05,800 --> 00:39:10,240
[Yu grunts, panting]

731
00:39:16,840 --> 00:39:18,400
I knew you were practicing here.

732
00:39:23,480 --> 00:39:24,600
-[thwacks]
-[Yu grunts]

733
00:39:28,760 --> 00:39:30,440
[Zhuo Zi] It's a weird swing.

734
00:39:31,800 --> 00:39:32,880
-[thwacks]
-[Yu grunts]

735
00:39:36,040 --> 00:39:37,120
Did Guan Yue

736
00:39:38,000 --> 00:39:39,360
teach you these techniques?

737
00:39:39,760 --> 00:39:40,880
He did.

738
00:39:41,280 --> 00:39:42,120
He's better than you.

739
00:39:42,480 --> 00:39:43,560
-[thwacks]
-[Yu grunts]

740
00:39:45,040 --> 00:39:47,040
[somber music]

741
00:39:48,960 --> 00:39:50,280
-[thwacks]
-[Yu grunting]

742
00:39:53,720 --> 00:39:54,600
Guan Yue.

743
00:39:56,680 --> 00:39:57,680
[snickers]

744
00:40:00,200 --> 00:40:01,960
[Zhuo Zi] How could you let Zhuo Yu

745
00:40:02,720 --> 00:40:04,800
be hurt like this?

746
00:40:19,600 --> 00:40:20,840
What did you want to talk about?

747
00:40:23,960 --> 00:40:25,000
[Zhuo Zi chuckles]

748
00:40:25,640 --> 00:40:26,560
Yan,

749
00:40:27,080 --> 00:40:29,360
do you know what match Guan Yue will play?

750
00:40:31,640 --> 00:40:33,880
My guess is the second singles.

751
00:40:37,360 --> 00:40:38,480
[snickers]

752
00:40:39,360 --> 00:40:41,080
This is all within my expectations.

753
00:40:49,560 --> 00:40:50,640
[sighs]

754
00:40:53,240 --> 00:40:54,280
Sorry, Zhuo Yu.

755
00:40:54,920 --> 00:40:56,160
Your target has escaped.

756
00:40:56,800 --> 00:40:58,760
I thought Zhuo Zhi was playing
the third singles.

757
00:41:00,440 --> 00:41:01,600
What's happening?

758
00:41:01,680 --> 00:41:03,720
I fell for Yan Zhiming's trick.

759
00:41:04,160 --> 00:41:06,880
He seems to be avoiding a duel
between the two of you.

760
00:41:07,360 --> 00:41:09,160
Don't your plans always work?

761
00:41:09,880 --> 00:41:10,880
[sighs]

762
00:41:11,720 --> 00:41:13,800
I didn't expect Yu Qing to be so cowardly.

763
00:41:13,880 --> 00:41:16,680
If Zhuo Zhi really loses to his brother,
it will be a total disgrace.

764
00:41:16,760 --> 00:41:17,840
What did you just say?

765
00:41:17,920 --> 00:41:19,600
[Yu] "Brother"? Don't I have a name?

766
00:41:19,680 --> 00:41:21,080
Sorry, my bad.

767
00:41:21,160 --> 00:41:22,960
There will be
other opportunities, Zhuo Yu.

768
00:41:23,360 --> 00:41:24,200
-[Yue] Now,
-[sighs]

769
00:41:24,280 --> 00:41:26,520
just focus on defeating that freshman.

770
00:41:26,600 --> 00:41:27,560
[Yue] Okay?

771
00:41:28,400 --> 00:41:30,120
-[Yu breathing deeply]
-[bones crack]

772
00:41:31,000 --> 00:41:32,040
Zhuo Yu.

773
00:41:34,680 --> 00:41:36,200
Consider it done, Guan Yue.

774
00:41:37,120 --> 00:41:40,320
But, if he's not as good as Zhuo Zhi,

775
00:41:41,080 --> 00:41:42,240
I'm going to be upset.

776
00:41:51,120 --> 00:41:52,960
-[thumps]
-[Yu pants]

777
00:41:56,040 --> 00:41:58,040
[upbeat music]

778
00:41:59,480 --> 00:42:00,560
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

779
00:42:00,640 --> 00:42:02,520
[pants]

780
00:42:25,120 --> 00:42:28,200
Is it your plan to have him play
against that freshman player?

781
00:42:28,600 --> 00:42:30,320
He's the bane of left-handers.

782
00:42:31,200 --> 00:42:32,520
Pitting him against Lu Xia

783
00:42:33,160 --> 00:42:34,680
secures our victory.

784
00:42:36,000 --> 00:42:38,120
It seems like you're
going for quick kills.

785
00:42:38,680 --> 00:42:41,040
If not, you wouldn't have asked me
to play doubles.

786
00:42:41,520 --> 00:42:46,040
If Siyang plays the first singles,
it might be disadvantageous for us.

787
00:42:46,240 --> 00:42:48,040
[Yue] Second doubles, 6-2.

788
00:42:48,720 --> 00:42:50,280
First doubles, 7-6.

789
00:42:50,760 --> 00:42:52,280
Third singles, 6-4.

790
00:42:53,240 --> 00:42:54,880
